%h1 Send Us Your Exercises!

%p
  While CodeWorkout allows you to author your own exercises, not all educators
  want to take the time to do this.
  = succeed ',' do
    %strong If you have exercises you want to share
  in the form of written tests, quizzes, or question banks,
  %strong We will import them for you
  as long as you are willing to share them publicly with others.
  E-mail your exercises to
  = link_to 'mailto:questionbank@vt.edu' do
    questionbank@vt.edu
  and we'll convert them for you!

%p
  All exercises you submit must be your own work, and will be released to
  others under the Creative Commons
  = link_to 'http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/' do
    Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International
  license.
